description:
"Stay Fresh for Less" 

JackThreads is the #1 shopping app for guys, delivering killer gear at up to 80% off daily to over 3 million members worldwide.

We scour the globe to unearth the freshest looks and deepest discounts available, then deliver them to you every day at noon; combining premium brands you already love with buzz-worthy newcomers. Whether it's graphic tees, tailored chinos, fresh kicks, man-cave essentials, or everyday basics - Jack's hooking you up with the gear you need NOW.
